name: Zillow Metrics (Zip Codes): Sold for Loss (%) - 90606,West Whittier-Los Nietos,CA
description: The percentage of homes that sold for less than the previous purchase price (e.g. a home purchased for $250k and then sold for $225k). This excludes foreclosure transactions. This data is calculated by Zillow Real Estate Research (www.zillow.com/research) using their database of 110 million homes.
